Title: Britney Grenier will be charged and sentenced in Russia!
Narrative:
Through an idiotic misstep by one of the best women’s basketball players in recent history, Russia has gained a significant bargaining chip to trade her for Russian nationals in prison in the United States.

Experts say that 99% of all criminal cases in Russia result in a conviction, namely because trials are more for show than anything else. What makes matters even more concerning for her is that this percentage is not broken down into run-of-the-mill criminal trials and politically significant ones like this.

But the worst fact of all is that she hardly even has a legitimate defense. The video plainly showed her bag containing a suspicious package of vape cartridges.

Always respect the laws of the country you are in. Especially in countries like Russia - if you ever want to see the light of day again.
